<title>CANADA: PanCanadian stock split approved.</title>
<headline>PanCanadian stock split approved.</headline>
<dateline>CALGARY 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>PanCanadian Petroleum Ltd said on Thursday that shareholders at the annual meeting approved a previously announced two-for-one split of its common shares.</p>
<p>The company said the record date for the split was May 8. The split will not alter Canadian Pacific Ltd 's 87 percent ownership of PanCanadian.</p>
<p>((Reuters Calgary Bureau 403-531-1624))</p>
